name: @waylay/isSensorDisabled
description:
helps to check which SynField sensors are disabled based on the property sensorsArray.
States
  • None - when all sensors are enabled.
  • Some - when some sensors are disabled and some are enabled.
  • All - when all sensors are disabled
  • Not Found - when sensorArray is empty

Properties
  • sensors[] - rawData from RetrieveHeadNodeSensors sensor

Raw Data
  • disabledSensors[]
  • enabledSensors[]
  • disabledSensorsNames : String (e.g. sensorAName, sensorBName)
  • disabledSensorsNames : String
